text: "Disco 2000" is a 1995 song by English alternative rock band Pulp and is the third single from their fifth studio album Different Class. It went to number 7 in the United Kingdom, number 8 in Scotland and Hungary, number 35 in Australia, number 2 in Iceland, number 14 in Austria and number 13 in Ireland. ==Track listings== * The liner notes mislabel the album mix of "Disco 2000" as the 7-inch mix. ==References== Category:1995 songs Category:Pulp (band) songs
title: Disco 2000 (song)
